</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-02-02-0370-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-03-02-02-0370-fn-0001">1</a>

   <p>See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-02-02-0330" class="document">Arnold to GW, 13 Nov. 1775</a>.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-02-02-0370-fn-0002-ptr" id="GEWN-03-02-02-0370-fn-0002">2</a>

   <p>Henry Caldwell (c.17351810), a former major in the British army who was lieutenant colonel of the British militia defending Quebec, lived at Sainte-Foy.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-02-02-0370-fn-0003-ptr" id="GEWN-03-02-02-0370-fn-0003">3</a>

   <p>See Arnold to Montgomery, this date, in <span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Kenneth Roberts, ed. &lt;i&gt;March to Quebec: Journals of the Members of Arnolds Expedition&lt;/i&gt;. New York, 1938. ]">Roberts, <span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">March to Quebec</span></span>, 9092.</p>

